comments: Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen and makes marginal contact to Porter Jr.'s (CHI) body that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Porter Jr. (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Fournier (ORL).
[Observable in enhanced video] LaVine (CHI) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Lopez (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and absorbs the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Porter Jr. (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lopez (CHI) briefly grasps Vucevic's (ORL) arm but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Porter Jr. (CHI) and Ross (ORL) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Augustin (ORL) and Markkanen (CHI) briefly engage and disengage following the dribble hand-off.
Dunn (CHI) maintains his pivot foot.
[Observable in enhanced video] Markkanen (CHI) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Gordon (ORL) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Markkanen (CHI).
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact to the arm of Fournier (ORL) at the end of the drive but the contact does not affect his ability to make the pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Vucevic (ORL) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Dunn (CHI) makes body to body contact with Augustin (ORL) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gordon (ORL) briefly puts an arm around the waist of Markkanen (CHI) but the contact his tactile in nature and does not affect his SQBR.
Markkanen (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RLB and RLS show Gordon (ORL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with LaVine (CHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
LLB shows Briscoe (ORL) makes incidental contact to the arm of Lopez (CHI) after the release that does not affect his play at the basket.
Lopez (CHI) has his arm resting on Iwundu's (ORL) right arm but the contact is incidental and he does not hold it down and prevent him from going for the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) has his arms extended when he sets the screen on Porter Jr. (CHI) but he collapses them and does not deliver the contact.
Selden (CHI) releases the inbound pass within five seconds.
Lopez (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Isaac (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.  The two players briefly engage and disengage following the screen.
LaVine (CHI) and Fournier (ORL) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Markkanen (CHI) and the two players briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
LaVine (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position defending Fournier (ORL) on the perimeter and he does not release his shot attempt before the game clock expires.
RAR shows Gordon (ORL) moves A to B and makes contact to the body of Markkanen (CHI) after the release that affects his jump shot attempt and ability to land safely.
